nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.automaton

Class TypeAutomaton

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.automaton.TypeAutomaton

  • public class TypeAutomaton
extends java.lang.Object
    Class is used to represent the type automaton. Type Automaton represents the structure that data instances in the provided solutions will follow. It comprises blocks of data types that are added to the memory and those that are being used by tools, as input.

    Labeling of the automaton is provided in /APE/res/WorkflowAutomaton_Implementation.png
    Author:
    Vedran Kasalica
